  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was one of those [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not rare but infrequent [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] lay people who insisted on remaining a layperson, but was a renowned rabbinic scholar, descendant, as he used to say, son after son after one of the-- of the great rabbis whose books are today still currently studied in the yeshivot, certainly in the Orthodox yeshivot.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] He was a rather unusual man in many ways, quite handsome, dressed in a kind of a semi-Hasidic style.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Very natty, because he was traveling, and his business was wine and liquor and beer wholesaler and exporter, above all.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The business main portion was export.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He used to have his clothes made in London.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] He was also a man of very big concepts, not very practical because his mind was always on his Talmudic studies.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think I could best indicate to you how [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he conceptualized all sorts of major business moves-- that while the [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Congress of the United States debated whether or not to withdraw the prohibition-- I don't remember what amendment to the Constitution it was.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think the 22nd Amendment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I, I, I really don't know the number.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My father already had two boatloads of wine on it-- and liquor on its way to the United States.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But, you know, he could conceptualize these major business moves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But for execution and for management, he had to rely entirely on my mother, who not only, of course, was more at home with Hungarian and understood administration and correspondence and cables and things of that kind, but was far more practical, in, in a certain sense, than my father was.",
      "word_count": 51
    }
  ],
